Today we stopped at some apple and pear trees just to get provisions. Of course we also grabbed some delicious thistles, mugwort and rush.
Thistles and mugwort are quite healthy, but what I've read about rush plants is quite amusing. Supposedly the only horses which eat them are starving horses 😅 and Zazou eats all the time. As you can see even during riding sessions. He is also quite fat, so I can disprove this theory.
